# T4 — never commit. Akshay-local data only. Claude refuses to read by name pattern.
# Particularly important for this repo: it is PUBLIC. T4 leaks here are externally visible.
# Matches any file containing `.local.`, `.private.`, `.real.`, or `.map.local.` in name.
*.local.*
*.private.*
*.real.*
*.map.local.*
# Belt-and-suspenders explicit names (covers leading-dot edge cases)
.thinking.local.md
.balance-sheet.local.md
.bitgo-equity.local.md
.portfolio-map.local.yaml
.wealth.local.md

